title: He-Man and the Masters of the Universe
description:
He-Man and the Masters of the Universe is an American animated television series produced by Filmation based on Mattel&#039;s successful toy line Masters of the Universe. It made its television debut in 1983 and ran until 1984, consisting of two seasons of 65 episodes each. 

I am posting some comics of He-Man and the Master of the Universe published by various companies. There are mini series published by DC and Marvel. Comics published by Image Comics are also there. Several Minis (comics are mini sized), which were sold along with Masters of the Univers Toys are also posted. Its a good addition to everyones collection. Enjoy and Seed
